author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Ben Caplan is a Canadian musician and I hadn't heard of him before, but one of my subscribers left a comment, advising me to listen and so I did. It has a great video which was filmed in Mexico, not Japan: I made that bit up. 

To listen to the song in its entirety, visit:  https://youtu.be/FRD0W2-tr64?si=j_hP92bNPGtivHQp
